Scalar API Reference
====================

This directory contains vendored assets from the Scalar project:

  Project: @scalar/api-reference
  Version: 1.62.4
  Source : https://github.com/scalar/scalar
  License: MIT (https://github.com/scalar/scalar/blob/main/LICENSE)

Files:
  scalar-reference.js  - dist/browser/standalone.min.js (UMD bundle)
  styles.css           - dist/style.css
  index.html           - Baldr-authored wrapper; contains the
                         __TITLE__, __SPEC_URL__, __JS_URL__,
                         __STYLES_URL__ and __CONFIGURATION__
                         placeholders rewritten at runtime when the
                         helper serves the page.

These files are embedded into the OpenApiExample binary at build time
via the `baldr_embed_scalar_assets` CMake function. They are not loaded
from a CDN at runtime.